>
  <h2>CMS Medicare Physician Fee Schedule (MPFS)</h2>
  <p>
    Primary source for Medicare allowed amounts by CPT/HCPCS code and geographic locality.
    Published by the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services (CMS). Updated annually
    (and sometimes quarterly for some files).
  </p>

  <h2>NCCI edits</h2>
  <p>
    National Correct Coding Initiative (NCCI) procedure-to-procedure edits help identify
    code pairs that Medicare typically does not pay separately when billed together.
    We use these as <em>possible</em> unbundling signals, not proof of error.
  </p>

  <h2>Hospital price transparency files</h2>
  <p>
    Hospitals publish machine-readable standard charges under federal transparency rules.
    We plan to incorporate these for hospital price comparison tools (rolling out after
    the Fair Price Calculator).
  </p>

  <h2>Update cadence</h2>
  <p>
    Data bundle versions and last-updated dates will be shown on each tool once live.
    Methodology pages will be updated when we ship new data releases.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
